        <mxCell id="instruction_box" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#ffffff;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=18;spacing=12;" value="Please complete this request: Prepare a duration repositioning proposal for Clearwater Bond Sleeve. Address the client objective, current portfolio facts, and policy constraints supplied in the context. ...&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2f6db3&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Present the output as before-and-after duration table.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#c88719&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Quality Verification] Compare current and pro forma duration with a 3.0 to 5.0 year range.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#c88719&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Quality Verification] Confirm investment-grade exposure remains at least 90%.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#7c4fb5&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Decision and Boundary] Recommend proceed, modify, or decline.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#2d8a57&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Evidence and Grounding] Avoid treating rate movements as certain.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Final work-product request ... &lt;font color=&quot;#9c6b2f&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;[Required Content Coverage] For any calculation or reconciliation, show source inputs, formula or comparison, result, and business implication.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="220" width="820" x="70" y="160" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
