        <mxCell id="response_box" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#333333;fillColor=#ffffff;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=17;spacing=12;" value="&lt;b&gt;Clearwater Bond Sleeve — Duration Repositioning Proposal&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Evaluate the proposal against the &lt;font color=&quot;#228b4e&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;3.0 to 5.0 year&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; range and the &lt;font color=&quot;#228b4e&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;90.00%&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; investment-grade threshold.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;Duration test&lt;/b&gt; | Current duration was &lt;font color=&quot;#c53b3b&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;not supplied&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ... &lt;font color=&quot;#c53b3b&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Duration comparison cannot be performed.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;IG exposure test&lt;/b&gt; | Current investment-grade exposure was &lt;font color=&quot;#c53b3b&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;not supplied&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt; ... &lt;font color=&quot;#c53b3b&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cannot confirm at least 90.00%.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#228b4e&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Recommendation: Modify. Do not proceed as presented.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
